# Project Title
HostelEase – Hostel Essentials Ordering System

# Overview
HostelEase is a MERN stack web application that helps hostel students purchase their essential needs 
(snacks, stationery, toiletries, etc.) easily from within the hostel. 
Admins manage the product catalog and track orders, while students can browse and place orders online.

# Tech Stack
- MongoDB
- Express.js
- React.js
- Node.js  

# Libraries / Tools
- Mongoose
- JWT
- bcryptjs
- multer / cloudinary (for image upload)
- dotenv
- axios
- cors
- React Router DOM
- Redux Toolkit (optional)

# System Phases

## Phase 1: Admin
Responsibilities:
- Manage products (add, edit, delete)
- Track and update student orders
- View order history and analytics

Functionalities:
1. Product Management
   - Add new product (name, price, image)
   - View all products
   - Edit / Delete products

2. Order Management
   - View all orders
   - Update order status (Pending → Processing → Delivered)
   - Cancel orders
   - View order history

## Phase 2: Student
Responsibilities:
- Browse products
- Place and manage orders
- Track order status

Functionalities:
1. Authentication
   - Register
   - Login

2. Product Browsing
   - View all available products

3. Order Placement
   - Place order for desired product
   - View order history
   - Cancel order before it is processed

# Models

## 1. User Model
- name: String
- email: String
- password: String
- role: String (enum: ['student', 'admin'])

## 2. Product Model
- productName: String
- price: Number
- image: String

## 3. Order Model
- orderName: String
- price: Number
- userId: ObjectId (ref: 'User')
- productId: ObjectId (ref: 'Product')
- status: String (enum: ['Pending', 'Processing', 'Delivered', 'Cancelled'])
- createdAt: Date (default: Date.now)

# Controllers

## User Controller
- registerUser
- loginUser

## Product Controller
- createProduct (admin only)
- getAllProducts
- updateProduct (admin)
- deleteProduct (admin)

## Order Controller
- placeOrder (student)
- getAllOrders (admin)
- getUserOrders (student)
- cancelOrder (student/admin)
- updateOrderStatus (admin)

# Routes

## Auth Routes
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login

## Product Routes
POST   /api/products              -> Create product (admin)
GET    /api/products              -> Get all products
PUT    /api/products/:id          -> Update product (admin)
DELETE /api/products/:id          -> Delete product (admin)

## Order Routes
POST   /api/orders                -> Place order (student)
GET    /api/orders                -> Get all orders (admin)
GET    /api/orders/user/:id       -> Get user-specific orders (student)
PATCH  /api/orders/:id/status     -> Update order status (admin)
DELETE /api/orders/:id            -> Cancel order (student/admin)

# Additional Features (Future Enhancements)
- Notifications for order updates
- Search & filter products
- Product categories (Snacks, Stationery, Toiletries)
- Inventory management (track stock)
- Admin dashboard with order analytics
- Payment gateway integration (future scope)

# Outcome
A complete hostel-based MERN web application 
that streamlines the purchase of essential items for students 
and simplifies order management for administrators.
